item.title: CVE-2015-8987|2024-08-06T08:36:30.829Z -- intel -- agent%20%28ma%29
item.description: Man-in-the-middle (MitM) attack vulnerability in non-Mac OS agents in McAfee (now Intel Security) Agent (MA) 4.8.0 patch 2 and earlier allows attackers to make a McAfee Agent talk with another, possibly rogue, ePO server via McAfee Agent migration to another ePO server.
